## Example Patterns

**Graph Pattern:**
```python
from strands.multiagent.graph import Graph, Node, Edge

graph = Graph(name="workflow")
graph.add_node(Node(name="step1", agent=agent1))
graph.add_node(Node(name="step2", agent=agent2))
graph.add_edge(Edge(source="step1", target="step2"))
```

**Swarm Pattern:**
```python
from strands.multiagent.swarm import Swarm

swarm = Swarm(name="team")
swarm.add_agent("expert1", agent1)
swarm.add_agent("expert2", agent2)
result = await swarm.execute("task description")
```
